#: resources/animate.glade:78
msgid "Animated"
msgstr "Animatsiyali"

#: resources/animate.glade:85
msgid ""
"Hue shows the peak magnitude s(n); brightness follows the traveling wave |"
"cos(arg z + φ)|, floored so nulls stay visible.\n"
"\n"
"Animated: bright regions sweep along the structure as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"Rang tusi s(n) choʻqqi kattaligini koʻrsatadi; yorqinlik esa yuruvchi "
"toʻlqin |cos(arg z + φ)| ni kuzatadi, nol nuqtalar koʻrinishda qolishi uchun "
"pastki chegara qoʻyilgan.\n"
"\n"
"Animatsiyali: faza siljigan sari yorqin zonalar tuzilma boʻylab siljiydi."

#: resources/animate.glade:86
msgid "Instantaneous"
msgstr "Momentan"

#: resources/animate.glade:96
msgid ""
"Diverging hue shows the instantaneous sign of the displayed quantity: cold "
"negative, hot positive; brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: regions swap poles as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"Ayiruvchi rang tusi koʻrsatilgan miqdorning lahzalik ishorasini bildiradi: "
"sovuq — manfiy, issiq — musbat; yorqinlik esa s(n) kattaligini tashiydi.\n"
"\n"
"Animatsiyali: faza siljigan sari zonalar qutblarini almashtiradi."

#: resources/animate.glade:97
msgid "Polarity"
msgstr "Qutblilik"

#: resources/animate.glade:107
msgid ""
"Cyclic hue wheel shows the phase angle arg z + φ; brightness carries the "
"magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: the whole wheel rotates as the phase advances."
msgstr ""
"Davriy rang gʻildiragi arg z + φ faza burchagini koʻrsatadi; yorqinlik esa "
"s(n) kattaligini tashiydi.\n"
"\n"
"Animatsiyali: faza siljigan sari butun gʻildirak aylanadi."

#: resources/animate.glade:108
msgid "Phase Hue"
msgstr "Faza tusi"

#: resources/animate.glade:118
msgid ""
"Diverging hue shows the instantaneous charge sign; brightness carries the "
"current envelope s(|I|).\n"
"\n"
"Animated: one view of charge and current a quarter cycle apart."
msgstr ""
"Ayiruvchi rang tusi zaryadning lahzalik ishorasini koʻrsatadi; yorqinlik esa "
"tok konvertini s(|I|) tashiydi.\n"
"\n"
"Animatsiyali: zaryad va tokning chorak davr farqidagi yagona koʻrinishi."

#: resources/animate.glade:119
msgid "Current + Charge"
msgstr "Tok + zaryad"

#: resources/animate.glade:136
msgid "Static"
msgstr "Statik"

#: resources/animate.glade:143
msgid ""
"Rainbow ramp of this frequency step's peak magnitude s(n) at full "
"brightness.\n"
"\n"
"Static: the phase-invariant baseline; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu chastota qadamining choʻqqi kattaligi s(n) toʻliq yorqinlikda kamalak "
"gradientida koʻrsatiladi.\n"
"\n"
"Statik: fazadan mustaqil asosiy chiziq; ijro paytida ranglar oʻzgarmay "
"qoladi."

#: resources/animate.glade:144
msgid "Amplitude"
msgstr "Amplituda"

#: resources/animate.glade:154
msgid ""
"Hue ramps the per-region standing-wave ratio: cold traveling, hot standing; "
"brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Static: a phase-invariant read; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"Rang tusi har bir zonaning turgun toʻlqin nisbatini aks ettiradi: sovuq — "
"yuruvchi, issiq — turgun; yorqinlik esa s(n) kattaligini tashiydi.\n"
"\n"
"Statik: fazadan mustaqil oʻqish; ijro paytida ranglar oʻzgarmay qoladi."

#: resources/animate.glade:155
msgid "Standing/Traveling"
msgstr "Turgun/Yuruvchi"

#: resources/animate.glade:165
msgid ""
"Hue ramps each segment's contribution to the selected far-field direction; "
"brightness carries the magnitude s(n).\n"
"\n"
"Static: a phase-invariant read; colors hold still during playback."
msgstr ""
"Rang tusi har bir segmentning tanlangan uzoq maydon yoʻnalishiga qoʻshgan "
"hissasini aks ettiradi; yorqinlik esa s(n) kattaligini tashiydi.\n"
"\n"
"Statik: fazadan mustaqil oʻqish; ijro paytida ranglar oʻzgarmay qoladi."

#: resources/animate.glade:166
msgid "Far-field Contribution"
msgstr "Uzoq maydon hissasi"

#: resources/animate.glade:180
msgid ""
"Power-law transfer n^γ of the normalized magnitude.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 1 is linear amplitude; γ = 0.5 expands weak regions; γ = 2 shows the "
"squared magnitude — |I|² is proportional to per-segment dissipated power "
"(and its radiated-power contribution via radiation resistance), |q|² to "
"stored electrostatic energy."
msgstr ""
"Normallashtirilgan kattalikning n^γ daraja qonuni transferi.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 1 — chiziqli amplituda; γ = 0.5 kuchsiz zonalarni kengaytiradi; γ = 2 "
"kvadrat kattalikni koʻrsatadi — |I|² har bir segmentda sarflangan quvvatga "
"(va nurlanish qarshiligi orqali nurlanish quvvatiga qoʻshgan hissasiga) "
"proporsional, |q|² esa toʻplangan elektrostatik energiyaga proporsional."

#: resources/animate.glade:181
msgid "Power"
msgstr "Quvvat"

#: resources/animate.glade:191
msgid ""
"Logarithmic transfer over a user range R, the RF-standard 20·log₁₀ amplitude "
"decibels.\n"
"\n"
"R sets the visible dynamic range; detail below the floor 10^(−R/20) clips to "
"the bottom color."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi diapazoni R boʻyicha logarifmik transfer — RF standarti "
"boʻyicha 20·log₁₀ amplituda desibellari.\n"
"\n"
"R koʻrinadigan dinamik diapazonni belgilaydi; 10^(−R/20) pastki chegaradan "
"past detallar eng past rangga kesiladi."

#: resources/animate.glade:192 resources/xnec2c.glade:11670
#: resources/xnec2c.glade:13045
msgid "dB"
msgstr "dB"

#: resources/animate.glade:202
msgid ""
"Inverse hyperbolic sine: linear below the knee k, logarithmic above.\n"
"\n"
"Keeps near-null currents visible while compressing strong peaks, like a lin-"
"log instrument scale."
msgstr ""
"Teskari giperbolik sinus: yumshatish tizza nuqtasi k dan past chiziqli, "
"undan yuqori logarifmik.\n"
"\n"
"Chiziqli-logarifmik asbob masshtabiga oʻxshab, deyarli nolga yaqin toklarni "
"koʻrinishda saqlagan holda kuchli choʻqqilarni siqadi."

#: resources/animate.glade:203
msgid "Asinh"
msgstr "Asinh"

#: resources/animate.glade:213
msgid ""
"μ-law companding, the telephony-standard bounded log curve.\n"
"\n"
"Lifts weak detail without a hard floor; 48.16 dB compression is the classic "
"μ = 255."
msgstr ""
"μ-qonun kompandingi — telefoniya standarti boʻyicha chegaralangan logarifmik "
"egri chiziq.\n"
"\n"
"Qattiq pastki chegarasiz kuchsiz detallarni koʻtaradi; 48.16 dB siqish "
"klassik μ = 255 qiymatiga mos keladi."

#: resources/animate.glade:214
msgid "μ-law"
msgstr "μ-law"

#: resources/animate.glade:224
msgid ""
"Reinhard rational compressor (1+k)·n/(n+k), the photographic HDR tone-map.\n"
"\n"
"Preserves midtones while rolling highlights off smoothly; k sets the knee."
msgstr ""
"Reinhard ratsional siquvchisi (1+k)·n/(n+k) — fotografik HDR tonlar "
"xaritasi.\n"
"\n"
"Oʻrta tonlarni saqlagan holda yorqin qismlarni silliq pasaytiradi; k tizza "
"nuqtasini belgilaydi."

#: resources/animate.glade:225
msgid "Reinhard"
msgstr "Reinhard"

#: resources/animate.glade:235
msgid ""
"Hyperbolic tangent soft limiter tanh(a·n)/tanh(a).\n"
"\n"
"Raises midrange contrast and saturates gently toward the peak, like "
"amplifier compression; a sets the steepness."
msgstr ""
"Giperbolik tangens yumshoq cheklovchisi tanh(a·n)/tanh(a).\n"
"\n"
"Oʻrta diapazon kontrastini oshiradi va kuchaytirgich siqilishiga oʻxshab "
"choʻqqiga tomon silliq toʻyinadi; a qiyalikni belgilaydi."

#: resources/animate.glade:236
msgid "Sigmoid"
msgstr "Sigmoid"

#: resources/animate.glade:246
msgid ""
"Identity: every magnitude renders at full brightness.\n"
"\n"
"The color projection alone carries the information."
msgstr ""
"Identifikatsiya: har qanday kattalik toʻliq yorqinlikda koʻrsatiladi.\n"
"\n"
"Faqat rang proeksiyasi maʼlumotni tashiydi."

#: resources/animate.glade:247 resources/settings/cairo_settings.glade:56
msgid "None"
msgstr "Yoʻq"

#: resources/animate.glade:259 src/rdpattern_ui.c:329 src/rdpattern_ui.c:337
#: src/rdpattern_ui.c:344
msgid "Near Field Animation"
msgstr "Yaqin maydon animatsiyasi"

#: resources/animate.glade:351
msgid ""
"Scrub the animation phase manually.\n"
"\n"
"Disabled while the animation is running."
msgstr ""
"Animatsiya fazasini qoʻlda boshqarish.\n"
"\n"
"Animatsiya ishlayotganda oʻchirilgan."

#: resources/animate.glade:368
msgid "φ 0°"
msgstr "φ 0°"

#: resources/animate.glade:382
msgid "Phase"
msgstr "Faza"

#: resources/animate.glade:405
msgid "Frames/Sec"
msgstr "Kadr/soniya"

#: resources/animate.glade:418
msgid "Animate Freq (Hz)"
msgstr "Animatsiya chastotasi (Hz)"

#: resources/animate.glade:491
msgid "Color projection:"
msgstr "Rang proeksiyasi:"

#: resources/animate.glade:505
msgid ""
"Select which physical quantity drives the hue and how brightness follows the "
"excitation phase.\n"
"\n"
"Static projections (Amplitude, Standing/Traveling, Far-field Contribution) "
"read without animating.\n"
"\n"
"Hovering an entry previews it live."
msgstr ""
"Rang tusini qaysi fizik miqdor boshqarishini va yorqinlik qoʻzgʻatish "
"fazasini qanday kuzatishini tanlang.\n"
"\n"
"Statik proeksiyalar (Amplituda, Turgun/Yuruvchi, Uzoq maydon hissasi) "
"animatsiyasiz oʻqiladi.\n"
"\n"
"Bandning ustiga sichqonchani olib borish uni jonli koʻrsatadi."

#: resources/animate.glade:532
msgid "Scale family:"
msgstr "Masshtab oilasi:"

#: resources/animate.glade:546
msgid ""
"Select the magnitude-to-color transfer family.\n"
"\n"
"Adjust its slider until the contrast reveals the range your inspection "
"needs.\n"
"\n"
"Hovering an entry previews it live."
msgstr ""
"Kattalikdan rangga transfer oilasini tanlang.\n"
"\n"
"Tekshiruvingiz uchun zarur diapazonni kontrast koʻrsatguncha uning sirgʻa "
"boshqaruvini sozlang.\n"
"\n"
"Bandning ustiga sichqonchani olib borish uni jonli koʻrsatadi."

#: resources/animate.glade:585
msgid "Gamma:"
msgstr "Gamma:"

#: resources/animate.glade:602
msgid ""
"Gamma exponent of the power transfer.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 0.5 expands weak regions, γ = 1 is linear, γ = 2 is proportional to "
"dissipated power for currents."
msgstr ""
"Quvvat transferining gamma koʻrsatkichi.\n"
"\n"
"γ = 0.5 kuchsiz zonalarni kengaytiradi, γ = 1 chiziqli, γ = 2 toklar uchun "
"sarflangan quvvatga proporsionaldir."

#: resources/animate.glade:624
msgid "Range (dB):"
msgstr "Diapazon (dB):"

#: resources/animate.glade:641
msgid ""
"Dynamic range R below the step peak mapped onto the color strip.\n"
"\n"
"The floor is 10^(−R/20) of the peak."
msgstr ""
"Qadam choʻqqisidan pastdagi R dinamik diapazoni rang tasmasiga moslanadi.\n"
"\n"
"Pastki chegara choʻqqining 10^(−R/20) qismidir."

#: resources/animate.glade:663
msgid "Softening:"
msgstr "Yumshatish:"

#: resources/animate.glade:680
msgid "Softening knee k: linear below k, logarithmic above."
msgstr ""
"Yumshatish tizza nuqtasi k: k dan past chiziqli, undan yuqori logarifmik."

#: resources/animate.glade:702
msgid "Compression (dB):"
msgstr "Siqish (dB):"

#: resources/animate.glade:719
msgid "Compression strength in dB; higher values lift weak detail."
msgstr "Siqish kuchi dB da; yuqori qiymatlar kuchsiz detallarni koʻtaradi."

#: resources/animate.glade:741
msgid "Knee:"
msgstr "Tizza nuqtasi:"

#: resources/animate.glade:758
msgid "Knee k of the rational soft-compressor."
msgstr "Ratsional yumshoq siquvchining k tizza nuqtasi."

#: resources/animate.glade:780
msgid "Contrast:"
msgstr "Kontrast:"

#: resources/animate.glade:797
msgid "Contrast steepness a of the tanh transfer."
msgstr "Tanh transferining a kontrast tikligi."

#: resources/animate.glade:830
msgid "Color gradient of the active projection and scale family."
msgstr "Faol proeksiya va masshtab oilasining rang gradienti."

#: resources/animate.glade:848
msgid "Brightness floor:"
msgstr "Yorqinlik pastki chegarasi:"

#: resources/animate.glade:866
msgid ""
"Minimum brightness under animation so elements cool toward this level "
"instead of vanishing to black."
msgstr ""
"Animatsiya paytidagi eng past yorqinlik — elementlar qora rangga toʻliq "
"soʻnib ketmasdan shu darajaga toʻxtaydi."

#: resources/animate.glade:877
msgid "Width from amplitude"
msgstr "Amplitudadan kenglik"

#: resources/animate.glade:882
msgid ""
"Scale wire segment width by the scaled amplitude envelope s(n), so strong "
"regions draw thick and nulls draw thin."
msgstr ""
"Sim segmenti kengligini masshtablangan amplituda konverti s(n) boʻyicha "
"oʻzgartirish — kuchli zonalar qalin, nol nuqtalar ingichka chiziladi."

#: resources/animate.glade:908
msgid "Overlays:"
msgstr "Qoplamalar:"

#: resources/animate.glade:919
msgid "Nodes/antinodes"
msgstr "Tugunlar/antitugunlar"

#: resources/animate.glade:924
msgid ""
"Mark current nulls (plus tick) and peaks (cross tick) on wire segments.\n"
"\n"
"Marks derive from the phase-invariant envelope, so they hold still while the "
"wave animates."
msgstr ""
"Sim segmentlarida tok nol nuqtalarini (plyus belgisi) va choʻqqilarini (xoch "
"belgisi) belgilash.\n"
"\n"
"Belgilar fazadan mustaqil konvertdan olinadi, shuning uchun toʻlqin "
"animatsiyalanganda ular oʻzgarmay qoladi."

#: resources/animate.glade:935
msgid "Comet"
msgstr "Kometa"

#: resources/animate.glade:940
msgid ""
"Ride a bright head on the instantaneous positive crest so wave motion reads "
"along each wire."
msgstr ""
"Toʻlqin harakati har bir sim boʻylab koʻrinishi uchun lahzalik musbat "
"choʻqqida yorqin bosh siljiydi."

#: resources/animate.glade:973
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "Tiklash"

#: resources/animate.glade:979
msgid ""
"Restore the color projection, scale family, and every family brightness "
"parameter to their defaults."
msgstr ""
"Rang proeksiyasi, masshtab oilasi va har bir oilaning yorqinlik parametrini "
"standart holatiga qaytaradi."

#: resources/animate.glade:994
msgid ""
"<b>Color</b> <i>— currents, charges, and fields shade the wires, patches, "
"and near-field vectors</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Rang</b> <i>— toklar, zaryadlar va maydonlar simlarni, patchlarni va "
"yaqin maydon vektorlarini boʻyaydi</i>"

#: resources/animate.glade:1025
msgid "None (geometry)"
msgstr "Yoʻq (geometriya)"

#: resources/animate.glade:1029
msgid "Show the bare structure geometry with no quantity coloring."
msgstr "Hech qanday miqdor rangisiz sof tuzilma geometriyasini koʻrsatish."

