#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10972
msgid ""
"Power transfer n^γ relative to this frequency step's peak.\n"
"γ = 0.5 expands weak regions, γ = 1 is linear amplitude, γ = 2 shows the "
"squared magnitude: |I|² is proportional to per-segment dissipated power (and "
"its radiated-power contribution via radiation resistance), |q|² to stored "
"electrostatic energy.\n"
"Adjust γ in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Bu chastota qadamining choʻqqisiga nisbatan n^γ quvvat transferi.\n"
"γ = 0.5 kuchsiz zonalarni kengaytiradi, γ = 1 chiziqli amplituda, γ = 2 "
"kvadrat kattalikni koʻrsatadi: |I|² har bir segmentda sarflangan quvvatga "
"(va nurlanish qarshiligi orqali nurlanish quvvatiga qoʻshgan hissasiga) "
"proporsional, |q|² esa toʻplangan elektrostatik energiyaga proporsional.\n"
"γ ni animatsiya dialogida sozlang."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10973
msgid "_Power"
msgstr "_Quvvat"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10984
msgid ""
"Logarithmic scale over a user-set range R below the peak.\n"
"Reveals weak detail that linear display hides; adjust R in the animate "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Choʻqqidan pastdagi foydalanuvchi belgilagan R diapazonida logarifmik "
"masshtab.\n"
"Chiziqli koʻrsatish yashiradigan kuchsiz detallarni ochib beradi; R ni "
"animatsiya dialogida sozlang."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10985
msgid "_dB"
msgstr "_dB"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10996
msgid ""
"Inverse hyperbolic sine transfer: linear below the softening knee k, "
"logarithmic above.\n"
"Adjust k in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Teskari giperbolik sinus transferi: yumshatish tizza nuqtasi k dan past "
"chiziqli, undan yuqori logarifmik.\n"
"k ni animatsiya dialogida sozlang."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10997
msgid "_Asinh"
msgstr "_Asinh"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11008
msgid ""
"μ-law companding transfer: lifts weak detail with bounded compression.\n"
"Adjust the compression in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"μ-law kompandirlash transferi: chegaralangan siqish bilan kuchsiz detallarni "
"koʻtaradi.\n"
"Siqishni animatsiya dialogida sozlang."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11009
msgid "μ-_law"
msgstr "μ-_law"

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:11020
msgid ""
"Reinhard rational soft-compressor with knee k.\n"
